{"tid":137631,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【符合國情】內銀因「逃廢債」損失過千億人幣 中銀監終出手整治","createTime":"2017-02-28T03:25:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-28T16:53:15.000Z","uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6f8e7bed26e74dd425a68f8bc6bf6d3fefba081e","tid":137631,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T03:25:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/28/112434_8c5d476e81ca6e2f348e5672c6ac5f6e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F28%2F112434_8c5d476e81ca6e2f348e5672c6ac5f6e.jpg&h=06c7daa0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n內地傳媒報道指，由於過去五年內地銀行被走數高達1,000億元（人民幣‧下同），涉及700多間企業，內銀稱之為「逃廢債」。有指中國銀協將向國務院滙報，並就相關問題展開調查，而中銀監亦會訂立新制度通知，打擊逃廢債。<br />\n<br />\n中國銀協公佈，逃廢債來自28個省份，其中北京、廣東及山東最嚴重，涉及700多間企業，高達1,000億債權化為烏有。當中北京自08年以來未執行的逃廢債達32億元。<br />\n<br />\n中國銀協表示，會將相關企業的資料公佈，並邀請中銀監，發改委及人民銀行等打擊逃廢債，而發改委已就成立「金融失信人員名單管理工作」通知，首季會有結果。中銀盛的法規部亦正制定打擊逃廢債的法例及通知。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56364099&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170228\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56364099%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170228&d=9l2h7zKZEd5x%2FdYTAZY3wi7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=4efb9371\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56364099%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170228&h=8b0ebddf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56364099&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170228</a>"},{"pid":"7d27cddb7287ae4ebcc8b85e1d31828de22bc545","tid":137631,"uid":55257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T05:07:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c541dddd06605444c451752c14a43f06f113f974","tid":137631,"uid":73092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T05:16:44.000Z","msg":"支爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5da3e9554e337d84a3c83fd11cf26670705aabe2","tid":137631,"uid":29773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T06:07:25.000Z","msg":"垃圾債券證券化<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b6c5a4df9f14b05bcac0f2afc679eaefc910c9b","tid":137631,"uid":42119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T06:09:06.000Z","msg":"IN支爆<br />\nWE TRUST<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbfb485c7df52d17b05650142964da621ccaf3f5","tid":137631,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T06:24:43.000Z","msg":"仲唔快d買國債救國"},{"pid":"6cc07bc04e5dafd3c066a33b61c45832f8dfe8f9","tid":137631,"uid":50374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T06:29:03.000Z","msg":"支爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a13c045a9c7c4cf4aae1e80a535b75935261bff1","tid":137631,"uid":49588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T06:37:08.000Z","msg":"還有香港的大水喉射住，未爆住！"},{"pid":"7c1db0523d0a9cf03185e2016811cf794825462f","tid":137631,"uid":29008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T16:53:15.000Z","msg":"繼續升<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}